'From Squeak2.7alpha of 9 November 1999 [latest update: #1698] on 10 December 1999 at 9:38:23 am'!"Change Set:		pkgBugDate:			10 December 1999Author:			Bob Arning- fix walkback when using cmd-key (cmd-b, e.g.) in the package pane of the PackageBrowser"!!StringHolder methodsFor: 'message list menu' stamp: 'RAA 12/10/1999 09:36'!packageListKey: aChar from: view	"Respond to a Command key in the package pane in the PackageBrowser"	aChar == $f ifTrue: [^ self findClass].	^ self classListKey: aChar from: view! !